{"tid":2003622,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"已經過咗一年，會員顯卡（#214534，私樓仔（已轉名））仲未話到比我知佢識用部macbook玩咩特異功能。。。","createTime":"2020-05-06T02:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T11:26:46.000Z","uid":175032,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"61f44e8361eebb5f6cf569d0cbc12236c7512c46","tid":2003622,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:54:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">校園台過街老鼠顯卡（214534）</span></span></strong><br />\n此人經常展現出自卑心作祟的心理狀態及相關行為表現。<br />\n過街老鼠顯卡（214534）認為只要透過發表一系列膠po取笑基層出身人士的屋住環境及社經地位限制，就可以藉此獲取優越感，行為相當幼稚可笑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大學時期就應該要分清楚自己既階級同圈子，以免他日後悔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/949951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/949951</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠並非窮人所生，乃書香世代大户人家所出，因戰亂先變窮人，所以只會窮一時！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/906769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/906769</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n校園台過街老鼠顯卡（214534）認為解決自卑的出路就是要依靠消費品物質提升自己的個人價值（主要是蘋果公司產品）。為保持自我價值及個人身份認同，校園台過街老鼠顯卡（214534）對其他人使用蘋果公司產品的行為非常敏感。過街老鼠顯卡曾經提出未有掌握apple公司産品MacBook特別功能的用家不配使用有關產品（而他至今亦未解釋上述的特別功能所謂何物）；而此人亦曾經提出使用蘋果公司產品的資格論：顯卡（214534）認為居住公屋的基層人士不應使用蘋果公司產品，反之只有包括自己在內的居屋/私樓住戶(未經證實）才有資格使用蘋果公司產品，作為其藍血身分的象徵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好心住公屋既人就唔好學人用蘋果產品喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/949237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/949237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n見好多廢柴買部MacBook 番黎但完全唔識啲功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/948681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/948681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最後希望校園台過街老鼠顯卡（214534）可以停止上述的幼稚行為，向專業人士尋求協助解決有關的自卑問題，並解答校園台各會員的問題：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n校園台過街老鼠顯卡（214534）話得比我知未啊<br />\n你識用部macbook玩咩特異功能啊<br />\n整唔整到核彈啊？</span>"},{"pid":"1efd63b4c6f44f90b2f6d72f8a124f00a04aa0db","tid":2003622,"uid":200521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:55:47.000Z","msg":"點少得GPDeal？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1a86d7eab90d11f8a5be036c5322aca12587d9","tid":2003622,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:56:10.000Z","msg":"睇返晨輝籽啲post先記得仲有顯卡依隻校台玩具"},{"pid":"98d9205acccf3e4031608666464bc1c2fee78b38","tid":2003622,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1efd63b4c6f44f90b2f6d72f8a124f00a04aa0db","tid":2003622,"uid":200521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:55:47.000Z","msg":"點少得GPDeal？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:57:28.000Z","msg":"Deal deal 係你條team跟開<br />\n48條乸型仔負責跟厹個case"},{"pid":"599550363349ddcdd95ba2114dda7773bcfd029c","tid":2003622,"uid":200521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98d9205acccf3e4031608666464bc1c2fee78b38","tid":2003622,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1efd63b4c6f44f90b2f6d72f8a124f00a04aa0db","tid":2003622,"uid":200521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:55:47.000Z","msg":"點少得GPDeal？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:57:28.000Z","msg":"Deal deal 係你條team跟開<br />\n48條乸型仔負責跟厹個case"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bca893d104e65f8bf13cfacd1f4fc718e1e801","tid":2003622,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26c2eec9d47364099a37a60b0120885ca8f7c9a","tid":2003622,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T04:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid